Customer Segmentation Project

Objective:
To classify customers into groups based on purchasing behavior and spending patterns.

Segments:

1. Low Value Customers
- Low spending
- Few purchases

2. Medium Value Customers
- Moderate spending
- Regular purchases

3. High Value Customers
- High spending
- Frequent purchases

Tools Used:
- Microsoft Excel

Outcome:
Successfully segmented customers and visualized customer groups using charts and dashboards.